      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "I'M MY DESIGN (8) turned in a modest effort most recently when sixth at this track over 342m behind She's Got Design (20.48) in a TG1-4W. Has good speed and can quickly clear the pack out wide. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. TRANSFORMATION (1) is mixing form lately, finishing out of the placings last time at Bendigo but was a Maiden winner two back at Shepparton. Good beginner and aided by the inside draw. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. ON THE STRIP (7) doesn't win out of turn. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing third (17.27) at Murray Bridge Straight. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Must be included in calculations. LEFEVRE GOLD (2) was out of the money here last time out but can bounce back.",
